Quality settings
================

These are the [CVars](Console) and other game features that change depending on which quality level you select in the system options menu.

<span align="absbottom">![](/images/images_2_23_D3square_25.png) Doom 3</span>
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  
*The information in this section is specific to [Doom 3](Doom\_3).*

| Doom 3                                                                         | Low  | Medium | High  | Ultra |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------|--------|-------|-------|
| [com\_machineSpec](Com\_machineSpec\_(cvar))                               | 0    | 1      | 2     | 3     |
| [image\_anisotropy](Image\_anisotropy\_(cvar))                             | 0    | 1      | 8     | 8     |
| [image\_downSize](Image\_downSize\_(cvar))                                 | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_downSizeBump](Image\_downSizeBump\_(cvar))                         | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_downSizeSpecular](Image\_downSizeSpecular\_(cvar))                 | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_ignoreHighQuality](Image\_ignoreHighQuality\_(cvar))               | 1    | 1      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_useCompression](Image\_useCompression\_(cvar))                     | 1    | 1      | 1     | 0     |
| [image\_useNormalCompression](Image\_useNormalCompression\_(cvar)) \*      | 2    | 2      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_usePrecompressedTextures](Image\_usePrecompressedTextures\_(cvar)) | 1    | 1      | 1     | 0     |
| [r\_mode](R\_mode\_(cvar))                                                 | 3    | 3      | 4     | 5     |
| [s\_maxSoundsPerShader](S\_maxSoundsPerShader\_(cvar))                     | 1    | 1      | 0     | 0     |
| Texture Budget                                                                 | 64mb | 128mb  | 256mb | 512mb |

<span align="absbottom">![Q4](/images/images_e_e8_Q4square_25.png) Quake 4</span>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  
*The information in this section is specific to [Quake 4](Quake\_4).*

| Quake 4                                                                        | Low  | Medium | High  | Ultra |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------|--------|-------|-------|
| [com\_machineSpec](Com\_machineSpec\_(cvar))                               | 0    | 1      | 2     | 3     |
| [g\_brassTime](G\_brassTime\_(cvar))                                       | 0    | 0      | 1     | 2     |
| [image\_anisotropy](Image\_anisotropy\_(cvar))                             | 1    | 1      | 4     | 8     |
| [image\_downSize](Image\_downSize\_(cvar))                                 | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_downSizeBump](Image\_downSizeBump\_(cvar))                         | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_downSizeSpecular](Image\_downSizeSpecular\_(cvar))                 | 1    | 0      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_ignoreHighQuality](Image\_ignoreHighQuality\_(cvar))               | 1    | 1      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_useCompression](Image\_useCompression\_(cvar))                     | 1    | 1      | 1     | 0     |
| [image\_useNormalCompression](Image\_useNormalCompression\_(cvar)) \*      | 2    | 2      | 0     | 0     |
| [image\_usePrecompressedTextures](Image\_usePrecompressedTextures\_(cvar)) | 1    | 1      | 1     | 0     |
| [r\_mode](R\_mode\_(cvar))                                                 | 3    | 3      | 4     | 5     |
| [r\_skipNewAmbient](R\_skipNewAmbient\_(cvar))                             | 1    | 1      | 0     | 0     |
| [s\_maxSoundsPerShader](S\_maxSoundsPerShader\_(cvar))                     | 1    | 1      | 0     | 0     |
| Texture Budget                                                                 | 64mb | 128mb  | 256mb | 512mb |

\* nVidia GeForce 3 and 4MX cards use palettized normal maps in Medium and Low quality settings so this CVar is set to "1" on these cards. All other supported cards use [DXT5](DDS\_(file\_format)) compression.

You can use the [listImages](ListImages\_(console\_command)) console command to keep tabs on the texture memory usage of each setting.

